<h1>Import Recipe from URL</h1>
<p><a href="/my_book">Back to My Book</a></p>

<p>Paste the URL of a recipe blog post or cooking website. We'll try to extract the recipe automatically using structured data, and fall back to AI if needed.</p>

<form action="/recipes/import" method="post">
  <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token %>
  <div>
    <label>Recipe URL</label><br>
    <input type="url" name="url" required style="width:500px;" placeholder="https://...">
  </div>
  <br>
  <button type="submit">Import Recipe</button>
</form>

<hr>
<p>Or <a href="/recipes/new">create a recipe manually</a>.</p>
